\id 2JN - Capanahua NT -Peru 2008 (DBL -2013) 
\h 2 JUAN 
\toc1 Juaman raanni joi, jahuen rabe sca 
\toc2 2 Juan 
\toc3 2 Jn 
\mt1 2 JUAN 
\mt2 Juaman raanni joi, jahuen rabe sca 
\c 1  
\s1 Noquen huetsahon shinanaibo 
\p  
\v 1 Pastoro hihxon tah hen mato qui nea quirica raanai, Papan caisai baquebon. Maton baquebo rihbi qui tah hen nea hahxonai. Matohon tah hen shinancoinai. Hea huestichinma bi Papan joi honanaibo rahsichin ta matohon shinancoinihqui.  
\v 2 Papan joi coin ta noque betan hihquish jascabihi sca noque betan hihyaxihquiqui. Jaa copi tah non matohon hihti shinanai.  
\v 3 Papan ta noque jahuen shinan hinantihiqui. Noquen jointi rihbi ta sirijabahintihiqui, noquehon shinanxon. Jahuen joi jan yohini quescabijaquin ta noquehon shinanihqui. Jahuen baque Jesucristo betan ta Papan noque jascajaxontihiqui. 
\p  
\v 4 Papan noque yohihi quescabihi caibo maton baquebo jihuetaiton merahax tah hen hihti jenimahi. Papan noque yohini quescabija ta jacanihqui.  
\v 5 Mato tah hen yohiscai, hea huetsabon. Joi behna mato yohiquin hahcajaxonma bi tah hen non nincamenoni joibi hen mato yohihi: Noquen huetsahon shinannahue.  
\v 6 Noquen Hihbaan noque yohini quescabijaquin hahnicahboxon tah non joni huetsahon shinanscai. Man nincamenoni quescabihi ta jan noque yohini joi qui, non joni huetsahon shinani jihuenon. 
\s1 Parannicabo 
\p  
\v 7 Hicha paranmisbo ta nihresscaiqui. Jaabo ta Jesucristo ta yorayahpahax jonishqui hihyamahiqui. Jascapahbo ta paranmis qui, Criston sinatahbo.  
\v 8 Coiramenahue. Maton tee man yohyomis. Jaa yohyoxonma bi noquen Hihbaan mato hinanyaxihqui jatihibi bihyanoxon coiramenahue. 
\p  
\v 9 Criston noque honanmani joiya banexonma bi jaa potabahini caresaibo ta noquen Papajomabo qui. Criston honanmani joiya banetaibo ta noquen Papayahpabo qui, jahuen baqueyahpabo rihbi ta jaabo qui.  
\v 10 Mato qui nocoxon bi jaa joi yohiyamahibo maton xoboho mapemayamanahue. Jascapahbo metsonyamarihbiquin.  
\v 11 Jascapahbo metsonxon tah non tiromajati yanapanai. 
\s1 Jahuen quirica queyonoxon jan yohihi 
\p  
\v 12 Hicha hen mato huishaxon yohiti jai bi tah hen quirica raanxon yohiti queenyamahi. Mato qui nocoti caxon mato yohuanquihnxon yohiti tah hen queenai. Jaatian tah hen jenimacointihi. 
\p  
\v 13 Papan caisai maton huetsabaan ta nenoxon mato man jascabi jayamahin, noque huetsabaan, hahquiqui.